trans-unit.source: Defines methods for reading the parts of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage" />.
The following example shows how to obtain an <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedPageReader> collection from an <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedDocumentReader>.
trans-unit.target: Следующий пример показывает, как получить <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedPageReader> коллекции из <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedDocumentReader>.

trans-unit.source: The sample also shows how to use the fixed-page reader to add a new <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragment> that defines the document structure of the page.
trans-unit.target: Образец также показано, как добавить новый с помощью средства чтения фиксированных страниц <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragment> , определяющий структуру документа страницы.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of all the color contexts on the page.
trans-unit.target: Возвращает коллекцию всех цветовых контекстов страницы.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" /> that includes every <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsColorContext" /> that is on the page.
trans-unit.target: Коллекция <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" />, куда входит каждый <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsColorContext" />, имеющийся на данной странице.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of all the fonts that are used on the page.
trans-unit.target: Возвращает коллекцию всех шрифтов, используемых на странице.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" /> that includes every <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsFont" /> that is on the page.
trans-unit.target: Коллекция <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" />, куда входит каждый <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsFont" />, имеющийся на данной странице.

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the resource.
Gets the color context for the resource that has the specified [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Возвращает цветовой контекст ресурса, имеющего заданный [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsColorContext" />.
The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the font.
Gets the font that has the specified [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].
The font that has the specified Uri.
The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the image.
Gets the image that has the specified [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].
The image that has the specified Uri.
The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the resource.
Gets the resource that has the specified [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].
The resource that has the specified Uri.
Use this method when you do not know the specific type of the resource with the specified [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Используйте этот метод, если не известен тип ресурса с заданным [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: When you do know the type, use one of the type-specific methods that is provided by this class.
trans-unit.target: Если известен тип, используйте один из методов определенного типа, предоставленные этим классом.

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the resource dictionary.
Gets the resource dictionary that has the specified [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].
The resource dictionary that has the specified Uri.
trans-unit.target: Словарь ресурсов с указанным кодом URI.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of all the images on the page.
trans-unit.target: Возвращает коллекцию всех изображений на странице.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" /> that includes every <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsImage" /> that is on the page.
trans-unit.target: Коллекция <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" />, куда входит каждый <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsImage" />, имеющийся на данной странице.

trans-unit.source: Gets the page number.
An <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> that represents the page number.
trans-unit.target: Значение типа <see cref="T:System.Int32" />, представляющее номер страницы.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintTicket" />, if a ticket exists, that is associated with the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage" />.
trans-unit.target: Возвращает <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintTicket" />, если существует билет, связанный с <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintTicket" /> that contains the default printing options for the page; or <see langword="null" /> if no <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintTicket" /> exists for the page.
trans-unit.target: Объект <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintTicket" /> содержащий параметры печати данной страницы по умолчанию, или значение <see langword="null" />, если у страницы отсутствует <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintTicket" />.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> part of an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] page, see chapter 2 in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] specification, which you can obtain at [XPS: Specification and License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).
trans-unit.target: Дополнительные сведения о <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> частью [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] см. в разделе Глава 2 в [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] спецификации, который можно получить в [XPS: спецификация и формировании](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of all the resource dictionaries for the page.
trans-unit.target: Возвращает коллекцию всех словарей ресурсов для страницы.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" /> of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsResourceDictionary" /> objects.
Gets the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragments" /> part of the markup of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] package.

An <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsStructure" /> that represents a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragments" /> element in an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] package.

For more information about the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragments> element of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] package, see chapter 9 in the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] specification, which you can obtain at [XPS: Specification and License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).
trans-unit.target: Дополнительные сведения о <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragments> элемент [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] пакет, в главе 9 в [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] спецификации, который можно получить в [XPS: спецификация и формировании](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).

trans-unit.source: Gets the thumbnail image, if a thumbnail exists, that is associated with the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage" />.
trans-unit.target: Получает эскиз, если таковой имеется, связанный с <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsThumbnail" /> that represents the image.
Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage" />.
A <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> that represents the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] for the page.
Gets an <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlReader" /> for the page.
An <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlReader" /> for the page.
